PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Servicies of JANICE COCHRANE, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation from the public service of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, effective October 3, 1998.
